{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I knew what was going on here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that was a very, very scary kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On top of that, these Russians, there's a song that I absolutely do not want to ever hear again, because they would take my cats-- well, that's another story, but I just thought about the cats.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They'd take my cats, put the cats on a phonograph that was going round and round and watch and laugh as the cat is holding on, you know, trying to not be thrown off by the centrifugal force.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the other thing they did is they liked this song and they played it over and over and over again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got so sick of it, but this was just evidence of the fact that they were very immature and, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what would I call it-- they were regular soldiers, and you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, this is now, this is now after the Russians liberated us, but not, not quite yet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there had to be a fight back and forth, as I said.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians now live in our building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now they shoot at the Nazis until the Nazis retreat, until one point in time when it was declared that war is over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was that intermediary time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was furious at both my father and Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Szekely because nobody lifted a finger to help her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I don't know who decided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would think it was my mother who decided that she thought she better fend for herself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It I guess it was '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if it was '45, then I was eight years old, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went back to the original apartment that we lived in.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
